  "description": "<p><em><strong>☄️</strong></em><strong>No experience required, on the job training provided. ☄️</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>📆 Work Schedule: 6 days week</strong><br /><strong>🕒 Total Hours: 44 Hours/Week</strong><br /><strong>💵 Salary: Earn up to $2,305/month</strong></p><p><br /></p><h2>🧾 <strong>Your Role:</strong></h2><p><strong>Cashier</strong></p><ul><li>Operate the <strong>cash register or POS system</strong> smoothly and accurately</li><li>Handle <strong>cash, credit, and debit</strong> transactions with confidence</li><li>Provide <strong>friendly assistance</strong> to customers with product questions or concerns</li><li>Keep the <strong>cashier counter clean and organized</strong>, ensuring a professional environment</li><li>Balance your <strong>cash drawer at the end of the shift</strong> and report any discrepancies</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>EA License No: 19C9611</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1433735 Teng Wei Mun (Celest)</p>",
